Typedef Documentation

typedef SAMRAI::solv::PVodeTrioAbstractVector* N_Vector
 

External linkage for vector kernel operations needed by the PVodeTrio nonlinear solver package. This source file must be compiled for any application that will use PVodeTrio and a vector kernel whose operations are provided in a subclass of the abstract base class solv::PVodeTrioAbstractVector.

NOTE: These function definitions assume that the vector data will be of type { double}. Also, the return type int is used here whereas in PVodeTrio "boole" is used (boole is #define'd to be int).
